#: /tmp/tmpz6m6l9ck.md:166
msgid ""
"Chat window is also where you can roll dice by sending commands. \n"
"**Rolisteam** embeds a powerful engine based on generic operator.  \n"
"Those operators can be combined to make computation in repect with game "
"mechanism to give you final answer easy to read.\n"
"To roll one die with 6 slides, the command is: **!1d6**"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpz6m6l9ck.md:168
msgid ""
"The exclamation mark is important, It marks the beginning of dice command "
"but it can be replaced by some other characters.  \n"
"**&** marks a secret command. Only you can see the result.  \n"
"**#** send command to the GM (and only him/her)."
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpz6m6l9ck.md:172
msgid "&2d6"
msgstr ""

#: /tmp/tmpz6m6l9ck.md:175
msgid "#2d6"
